### Pre-PR Agent Testing

Before creating a PR that modifies Calor compiler, parser, or verification:

```bash
./tests/E2E/agent-tasks/run-agent-tests.sh
```

All tasks must pass (2/3 runs succeed). If tests fail, investigate before proceeding.

### File Types
- `.calr` - Calor source files (**use this for all code**)
- `.g.cs` - Generated C# files (never edit)
- `.cs` - Legacy C# files (**convert to Calor before modifying**)

